		<RichText x="1411" y="223" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威将剑朝向玩家，并蓄势冲向玩家，造成<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#b8b8b8">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威侧身插刀，拔刀时旋转一圈半，造成2段<span color="#ff9999">66.6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#b9b9b9">66.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威斜拿刀刃，抵挡前方任何攻击，免疫击飞，持续一段时间后放下。该状态下不免疫冻结和石化，处于冻结或石化状态下仍可受伤。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/海乱鬼%B7炎威.assets/Image_14.png')" x="1392" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/海乱鬼%B7炎威.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1392" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/海乱鬼%B7炎威.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1391" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威进行3段的普通攻击，每段攻击都造成<span color="#ff9999">46.6%</span><span>/</span><span color="#b9b9b9">46.6%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威将刀刃附上火元素，附魔完成后进行一次下劈，造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，附魔持续30s，不可被元素反应消除。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="433" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">炎威举着刀直接跳起来，朝下劈，造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>/</span><span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害，当处于火附魔状态时跳劈纵向范围提升50%，并且留下高温地面，接触持续造成</span><span color="#ff9999">20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="895" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">当附近有海乱鬼倒下时，短时间50m内战斗状态下的海乱鬼会进入「忿恨」状态：<span color="#ffbfbf">立即恢复50%生命值，免疫冻结和石化</span><span>。炎威进入此状态后，无论刀是否有火附魔，攻击均造成</span><span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
