		<RichText x="66" y="1200" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="266" height="20" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">拔刀入战时获得80%减伤，持续约4s。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1086" width="897" height="120" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="32" fontWeight="bold" color="#ff9672">固有天赋：火舞<br/><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">进入「忿恨」状态的海乱鬼·炎威会施放不同的固定招式COMBO：<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff7272">COMBO1：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">惟神术&gt;冲击&gt;冲击；</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff7272">COMBO2：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">惟神术&gt;冲击&gt;跃击&gt;冲击；<br/></span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff7272">COMBO3：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">惟神术&gt;跃击&gt;冲击；</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ff7272">COMBO4(不仅限于忿恨)：</span><span fontSize="24" color="#ffffff">跃击&gt;刀法(前两段)。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
